title: DryFever PhotoDeduper v1.2.0
description:
DryFever PhotoDeduper v1.2.0

Easy and comfortable way to find and delete duplicate photos and images !


Find similar images and file copies

Find both exact and similar duplicates.

Auto mark
Tool to automatically mark photos for deletion based on a user defined rule.

Sort groups
Sort duplicate groups by total file size of images, duplicate count or folder.

Auto cache
Save images data for much faster subsequent search.

Result list view modes
Select thumbnail, gallery or detailed view.

Official Website: http://photodeduper.com/
